@DATABASE "Exolon"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - E - Exolon"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - E
                   ====================================

                                  Exolon
                                  ======


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives  " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(40221,60)"}        40221,60
@{"Immunity        " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(38120,201)"}        38120,201
@{"Double Fire     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(33663,0)"}        33663,0
@{"One Shot        " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(44074,0)"}        44074,0
@{"Mines Don't Kill" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(40110,0)"}        40110,0
@{"Infinite Rockets" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(37397,0)"}        37397,0
@{"No Cannon Fire  " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(36831,24)"}        36831,24
@{"No Flying Aliens" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(42330,201)"}        42330,201
@{"Lot of Aliens   " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(42330,0) ZXAMPoke(42336,24)"}        42330,0:42336,24
@{"Fast Explode    " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(35456,0) ZXAMPoke(42338,0) ZXAMPoke(36845,0) ZXAMPoke(38221,0)"}        35456,0:36845,0:38221,0:42338,0
@{"??????????      " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(31646,0)"}        31646,0

                         Note:- The Immunity hack doesn't appear to work against
                                cannons or flying aliens, so I doubt it works
                                at all. However, I left it in just in case it
                                does work on some later level or whatever..
       
                                I honestly don't know what the "One Shot" POKE is
                                for, as you always start with one shot anyway??

                                The "Mines Don't Kill" POKE doesn't appear to
                                work either :(

                                The Fast Explode POKE make the grenades detonate
                                immediately. It doesn't look as nice, but it's
                                handy if you're playing on a full screen as it
                                doesn't SLOOOWWW the game down so much..

                                Just to state the blindingly obvious, you can't
                                select "Lots Of Aliens" and "No Aliens" at the
                                same time :)

                                Redefine keys as @{B}ZOBRA@{UB} for Infinite Lives

                                                                         Rastan.
@endnode
